English: Door has no Power, activate reserve power generator {0} to regain power
Description: A text that informs the player that the door they're trying to open has no power (electricity) and that they will need to activate a reserve power generator in order for the door to work. "{0}" will be replaced by the ID of the power generator that needs to be activated, do not alter those characters; just make sure they are in the gramatically correct position in the sentence.

Italian.Translation: La porta non è alimentata, attiva il generatore elettrico di riserva {0} per ripristinare l'elettricità

German.Translation: Tür hat keinen Strom, Reserve-Stromgenerator {0} aktivieren, um den Strom wieder einzuschalten

Spanish.Translation: La puerta no tiene energía. Activa el generador de reserva {0} para recuperar energía.

Russian.Translation: Дверь не подключена к источнику питания. Включите резервный генератор {0}, чтобы подать питание

Portuguese_Brazil.Translation: Porta sem energia; ative o gerador de energia reserva {0} para recuperá-la

Polish.Translation: Drzwi są pozbawione zasilania, uruchom rezerwowy generator mocy {0}, aby je przywrócić

Japanese.Translation: ドアに電力が通っていない。予備発電機 {0} を起動して電力を復旧しろ

Korean.Translation: 문에 전력이 공급되지 않습니다. {0} 예비 발전기를 작동해 전력을 공급하세요

Chinese_Traditional.Translation: 門沒有電源，啟用備用發電機{0}以恢復電力

Chinese_Simplified.Translation: 门没电了，激活备用发电机{0}以充电
